Key personalities and media were last week treated to a session of wine tasting and food pairing by visiting Nederburg s red winemaker Samuel Viljoen backed by Fairmont The Norfolk s executive chef Aris Athanasiou. It was an amazing taste experience and perfect culinary performance. Guests were also presented with a wine tasting note sheet with descriptions of the food the chef had paired with the various selection of Nederburg wines.At the event were Fairmont The Norfolk general manager Moshi Perera, KWAL mananging Carlos Gomez, Hallmark advertising s Louiza Wangui and Carole Mandi Media marketing manager Nailantei Kenga.